{"tid":739865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將闖超市狗掟落地兼腳踢　綜援漢虐畜罰$1000","createTime":"2018-07-12T11:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T12:13:36.000Z","uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"654308d918e01140dc113faa68dd938ae1a9c45c","tid":739865,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"53歲綜援漢去年9月24日在屯門寶田邨一間超市內，看見一隻啡色芝娃娃犬疑誤闖超市，但超市職員只圍着該犬，未有把犬趕走，他遂舉起該犬試圖扔出店外但不果，繼而再伸腳踢中該犬，過程被市民用手機拍片並上載到網上。涉案男子事後被警方票控一項虐畜罪，今(12日)在屯門法院認罪，判罰款1000港元。 <br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告呂偉倫於事發2天後被捕，他在警誡下承認有舉起該犬，然後該犬掙扎跳到地上，之後他把腳伸向該犬並觸及該犬。愛護動物協會的動物行為顧問獸醫看過市民在現場所拍攝片段後，認為被告的涉案行為已屬殘酷對待。"},{"pid":"6a760dee5e00b1f9dfeb7bd32470f0adac670e02","tid":739865,"uid":134683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T11:57:45.000Z","msg":"咬老綜交罰款有冇津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0416aa95c1ecdfdc4132f97a4ecd320381aac605","tid":739865,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56f78bca70154a266a26cd7fa89b5503cabddd04","tid":739865,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"芝娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8883c3b236fabd120339a12b969af1a14046df9d","tid":739865,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"$1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c502171c1c6d5fb67d33b228b2da8b4c728584b","tid":739865,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"原來成年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d7d494a7d0b051eab8af00f8b78d44668280e2","tid":739865,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"納dee<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a